---
layout: default
---
%html
  %head
    %title Courtney's Creations
    %link{:href => "font/coysfont.css", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}
    %link{:href => "css/style.css", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}
  
  %body
    .container
      .under-construction
        This site is still under construction. Check back soon for updates.
      .banner-top
        %img{src: "img/banner_top.png"}

      .row-fluid.blurb-row
        .slogan.blurb
          %h1 
            I make cute, customized designs for weddings and your special occasions.

      .row-fluid.blurb-row
        .span8.blurb.blurb-tall
          %img{src: "img/weddings.png"}
        .span4.blurb.blurb-tall
          %br
          %h1 Wedding stationery
          %p save-the-date cards
          %p invitations
          %p programs
          %p menus
          %p thank-you cards
      
      .row-fluid.blurb-row
        .blurb.blurb-short
          %h1 Special Occasions
          %p 
            birthdays, baby showers, mother's day, father's day, valentine's day, holidays, anniversaries, graduations, thank-yous, get-well wishes, etc

      .row-fluid.blurb-row
        .span4.blurb.blurb-tall 
          %h1 Family portraits
        .span8.blurb.blurb-tall 
          %img{src: "img/family_portrait.png"}
      
      .row-fluid.blurb-row
        .blurb.blurb-short
          %h1 How it's done
          %p
            Send in a current photo that really captures you or the recipient. If you have any specific features (birthmark, unique hairstyle, etc) make sure that the photo highlights it. Feel free to send me more than one. 

      .row-fluid.blurb-row
        .blurb.blurb-short
          %h1 Contact me:
          %p
            For more information, to receive a quote, or to place an order - please contact me at: 
            %a{href: "mailto:courtneyscustomizablecreations@gmail.com"}
              courtneyscustomizablecreations@gmail.com

      .banner-bottom
        %img{src: "img/banner_bottom.png"}
